title: Kenny Vs Spenny 410 - Who Can Commit The Most Crime
description:
Possessing a natural criminal mind, Kenny tries to break every law in the book, while Spenny tries to commit politically correct crimes and unleash his inner criminal.

Hey everyone, here&#039;s the season 4 finale.  Last Tuesday was New Year&#039;s day, so there was no episode on Showcase.  They were playing movies all night.  I suppose the fat-suit episode may have been aired on the Friday night &#039;repeat&#039; timeslot, but I forgot to tune in.  Although up until last night, showcase.ca was advertising the fat episode as airing tonight, so who knows.  Hopefully it&#039;ll get shown again soon.
